body:
Hey guys im an OCE player called Moltenstorm (IGN) trying to entertain you guys and show how i play illaoi and all of the ways i do it in.
with Season 9 Preseason starting darkharvest is now a highly sort out rune for illaoi.
 now ill bring this to the test and show you guys how string this rune is and see if this is the future for illaoi,
Watch as illaoi the kraken priestess Slams the Fury of the gods all over this Season 9 Preason montage to show who's boss in season 9.
Give a like and sub :).
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCpMCtY1YLInjfauQC17xrRA?view_as=subscriber

replies.body:
I tried new dark harvest on Illaoi for the first time earlier today (I only ARAM, so you play what you get), and got honoured by my entire team at the end of a 13 minute win. It's sick.I don't even play Illaoi much, but I'll definitely be trying that again.
I couldn't watch more than 2 mins of your vid, because I cba muting it and putting my own music on (2 mins is all I can stand of that type of music).
